drawnet.lib.ddl
Class Parent

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.ddl.Parent

public class Parent
extends java.lang.Object

A Parent object contains the ElementType defined to be parent of an element. It may also contain instructions to hide elements, hide properties, element aliases and property aliases valid for that parent.
